Source: syschangemon
Section: python
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Erno Rigo <erno@rigo.info>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), python, dh-virtualenv (>= 0.11)
Standards-Version: 3.9.5

Package: syschangemon
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.16.1), python2.7 | python2.6, ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: system change monitor
 Periodically collect system configuration (eg. conffiles in /etc, binary files in /sbin, etc.)
 for changes. If changes are found it sends text and html reports to predefined email addresses.
 You can think about this software as a mix of etckeeper, tripwire, samhain or fcheck.


